Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:06.06,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Drawn by a landscape as white as snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.61,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}I'm headed toward an unseen world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.54,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I've been traveling while lost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Under this gray sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.42,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Every day with new maps, stained with my many dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.80,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wonder if someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.84,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Even with these tiny steps of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.93,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I'll be able to travel beyond those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.56,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I put on a bold front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.10,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}End up hurting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I feel empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.73,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's started to rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.90,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And the raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.11,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Began to repeat their scattered reflections.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.99,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}These straight rays of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.70,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Start to cross one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.29,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}And without telling anyone where they're headed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.58,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Across the endless distances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They pass through all matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:14.01,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I burn these faint afterimages onto my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.92,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Under this sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.72,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}Wherever I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.06,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I should be able to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.85,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}The unseen world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:06.06,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)}{\blur3}真っ白な景色にいま誘われて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.61,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}僕は行くよ　まだ見ぬ世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.54,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}迷子のまま旅していた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}鼠色の空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.42,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}日替わりの地図 いくつもの夢が滲んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.80,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}いつかはさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.84,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}ちっぽけな僕のこの歩幅でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.93,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}あの雲の向こうまで行けるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.56,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.10,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}キズついた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}心透かしたように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.73,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}降り出した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.90,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雨粒たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.11,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}乱反射繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.99,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}真っ直ぐな光が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.70,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}交差して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.29,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}行き先も告げぬまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.58,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}突き抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:14.01,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}淡い残像　両目に焼きつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.92,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}この空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.72,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}どんなとこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.06,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}届くはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.85,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}まだ見ぬ世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:06.06,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Masshiro na keshiki ni ima sasowarete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.61,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Boku wa yuku yo mada minu sekai e
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.54,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Maigo no mama tabi shiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Nezumiiro no sora no shita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.42,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Higawari no chizu ikutsumo no yume ga nijindeita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.80,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Itsuka wa sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.84,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Chippoke na boku no kono hohaba demo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.93,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Ano kumo no mukou made yukeru kana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.56,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsuyogatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.10,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kizutsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Kokoro sukashita youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.73,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Furidashita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.90,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Amatsubu tachi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.11,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Ranhansha kurikaesu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.99,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Massugu na hikari ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.70,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kousa shite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.29,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Yakusaki mo tsugenumama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.58,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Doko made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsukinukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:14.01,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Awai zanzou ryoume ni yakitsukete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.92,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kono sora no shita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.72,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}Donna toko ni itemo
