Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.85,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}Mada minu sekai e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:33.28,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,657)}{\fad(500,0)}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:37.37,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to act tough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.17,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scribbling someone made...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.97,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,On the wall, of a flower is swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.56,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.85,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we both lose and gain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.27,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,By embarking on this long, long path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.94,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}And though there may be days loneliness strikes and makes us weep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:16.45,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's transform our tears and pains to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.46,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's light a candle to illuminate our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.59,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll hold our small hands over the fire to create stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:32.80,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And an eternity that shines so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:38.18,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewells may be unavoidable,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:44.11,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yet the seasons continue to change obliviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.19,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose myself, I'll continue to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.24,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.49,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}That's the only thing I'd like to never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:37.37,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,強がらなくていいんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.17,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが描いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.97,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,壁の落書きの花が　揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.56,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,自分らしさなんて, 誰もわからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.85,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,長い長い道の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.27,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,失くしたり, 拾ったり,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.94,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}急に寂しくなって, 泣いちゃう日もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:16.45,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}涙も　痛みも　星に変えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.46,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}明日を照らす　灯りをともそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.59,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さな手かざして　ふたりで作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:32.80,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,星屑を　強く光る永遠を探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:38.18,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,さよなら　いつかは来るかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:44.11,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}季節はそれでも巡り巡ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.19,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さく迷っても　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.24,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,君と歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.49,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}それだけは変わらないでいようね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:37.37,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaranakute iindane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.17,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka ga kaitetta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.97,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabe no rakugaki no hana ga yureru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.56,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibunrashisa nante dermo wakaranaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.85,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai nagai michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.27,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakushitari hirottari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.94,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kyuu ni samishikunatte naichau hi mo arukedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:16.45,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Namida mo itami mo hoshi ni kaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.46,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ashita wo terasu akari wo tomosou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.59,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisana te kazashite futari de tsukurou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:32.80,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshikuzu wo tsuyoku hikaru eien wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:38.18,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayonara itsuka wa kurukamoshirenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:44.11,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kisetsu wa soredemo meguri megutteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.19,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisaku mayottemo aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.24,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi to aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.49,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}Sore dake wa kawaranaideiyoune
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That was so exhausting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They were watching us the whole time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.20,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fu and Ran Fan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.12,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.83,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the young master!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:50.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.80,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have gone missing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.80,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... The instant I take my eyes off him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.64,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.81,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.81,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he hasn't collapsed somewhere like last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Good riddance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.36,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.44,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Young master! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.50,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,There's something... odd about this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.97,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. I came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.27,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.48,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,From the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.48,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, it's the cigarette kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.11,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing? Were you even able to beat him once?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.40,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.74,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,This game is pretty boring, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.41,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can go cut people up if it's just at night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.83,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.96,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could you at least... bring that Hawkeye lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.54,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll mention it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.63,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer do I have to watch over this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.13,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,What did the Colonel say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.97,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry for putting you in charge of such a dangerous task."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.52,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't worry about military duty, though."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.73,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,"I've marked you down as absent due to illness."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:38.19,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,"However, you're as good as dead if a civilian\Nor someone from the military besides us finds you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.23,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,...is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.07,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Any good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.24,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.66,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.62,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I got a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.71,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,She really helped me out when I was struggling with the transfer and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.04,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a babe, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.13,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think I'd enjoy cutting her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.22,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.01,Default-alt,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.47,Default-alt,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.43,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.68,Default-alt,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.56,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,F-Food...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.72,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.60,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Where's he from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.48,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,What? You came from Xing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.98,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.36,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's your certificate of entry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.45,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Make way! Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.49,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal entrant coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.74,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Young master! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.25,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,He's passed out somewhere... I just know he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go say hi to the military first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I think I'll go visit Mr. Hughes' place first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.05,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see Miss Gracia and Elicia, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head over there afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.81,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:02.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Lt. Colonel Hughes uncovered\Nmore information about the stone for us since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Führer President warned him to stay out of it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give him the information we obtained, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Lt. Colonel should be at the military chambers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:39.69,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sheska?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:40.94,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sheska!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.73,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.07,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You have the key to that room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.74,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.28,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Room 3, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.66,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,I've kind of made a mess in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.16,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I just need to grab some documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.00,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.17,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean it up right away, so please give me a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:05.01,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll come get it later, so please finish by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.92,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.02,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.86,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:33.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,How many minutes was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.62,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say about ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time before the army council.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:47.88,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse my unsolicited advice, but perhaps\Nyou should rest instead of straining yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.84,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.43,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Colonel Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.44,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning, Captain Focker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.31,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sheska.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.65,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,But why was the Colonel here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.07,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.65,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,The door to the archives is open, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.07,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! The truth is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.41,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, the colonel railroaded through, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.87,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.16,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:24.08,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what he was looking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.17,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,Any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.55,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details either,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.93,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,but he asked me whether there were\Nany documents concerning Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.68,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,That, and the murder of Brigadier General Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:44.44,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to the Brigadier General that I got a job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.61,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.11,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's a lot of work to do today as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.20,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:56.78,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.93,Default,Foc,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sheska.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.93,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.60,Default,Shes,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.37,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.08,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Did you perhaps lose some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:49.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You were injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.22,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Just some trouble down south.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.68,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.39,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I met the Elric Brothers while I was down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.77,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence. They were meeting their master, who lives in Dublith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.15,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told them about Hughes' death?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.91,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No, I couldn't bring myself to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.24,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Research Laboratory 5 and the philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients to the stones are live humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He was such an accommodating guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:38.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx99}He probably stuck his nose into what the Elric Brothers were researching and uncovered something he shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.55,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you won't tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:49.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out Hughes died because he got involved with them, they'd be devastated...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.57,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,And you know too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:09:59.95,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.45,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows who could be listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.21,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lieutenant Hawkeye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.64,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you here, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I was transferred to Central effective last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you? What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just collecting some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We were also thinking about going to say hi to Lt. Colonel Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He decided to retire to the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:03.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to take over the family business along with his wife and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.64,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We were looking forward to seeing him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump the gun and do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.09,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Treating them like children only at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They don't need to know right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:43.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if there are fewer obstacles for those brothers to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.47,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll find out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:55.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to call\NMajor Armstrong soft-hearted, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.86,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Soft-hearted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.28,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So the Lt. Colonel isn't around, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let Winry know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,She's headed for his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.13,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.72,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We heard about Lt. Colonel Hughes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.56,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.47,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There was so much I wanted to say to him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we had a chance to have a proper farewell with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.69,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,No one contacted you about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.73,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.07,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,The army gave him a proper farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's nice of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.91,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:53.66,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you may have heard this already, but he was specially promoted two ranks to the rank of Brigadier General.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Specially promoted two ranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.59,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He was specially promoted for retiring to the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.03,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.40,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! Why was he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:51.85,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Brigadier General Hughes was murdered by someone soon after you were released from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.06,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't caught the perpetrator yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged him into this! Lt. Colonel Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.21,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Well, careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.17,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to drop by if you ever come to Central again. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.26,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Alphonse, you can't eat with that armor on, can you? {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.59,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You guys probably haven't booked a place to stay at yet, right? {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.26,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,If so, stay at my place. {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.36,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who needs to face them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It concerns both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What if-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:32.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We chose to get our bodies back no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:38.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,but if people end up dying because of it, I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.67,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Winry just came by, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:03.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to tell you, Miss Gracia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.40,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Something to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:08.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And to Winry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.70,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,So my husband uncovered something about these philosopher's stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:25.46,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,And his death is the murderers' way of saying "don't meddle in our affairs"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We basically dragged him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:44.48,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,If he died while trying to help someone, then that's just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:50.73,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been a meddling, accommodating kind of guy, and he'd always end up losing things due to his kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.57,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think he's ever regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.33,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Even till the moment of his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.92,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:13.17,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,If you two give up here, it'd mean\Nmy husband's death was completely meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:20.10,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's impossible with the philosopher's stones, there may be other ways, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gracia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.90,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Move forward on the path you're content with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.16,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.16,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't cry, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're in there, right, Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The dining hall's going to close soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:54.69,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to function without food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.20,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm heading back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Apple pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.84,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced making it a few times since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:18.21,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to brag, but I've gotten really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.72,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's nowhere near as good as Miss Gracia's, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.35,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.98,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Mr. Hughes to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.96,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel is digging around\Nfor information about Hughes' death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.46,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's discovered anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.63,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:00.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:06.47,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,We moved him to Central to keep an eye on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.68,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Can't he just behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.31,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,He's a precious candidate for sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.31,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't gotten any information out of your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.19,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.32,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell if he's foolish or able.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.15,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go hunt for some information again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.16,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:32.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Gluttony! Don't leave this place a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.46,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lust?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:40.84,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We just need the Flame Alchemist to behave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.09,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.34,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you up for taking another measure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.85,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Got something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:54.85,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The best way to shut up an annoying dog is to give him some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.78,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Maria Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:05.20,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Henry Douglas from military police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.82,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.70,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.08,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Your sidearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.54,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:23.17,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Your name has been called as a\Nmaterial witness in the murder of Maes Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.63,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.64,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,You can explain yourself later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.14,Default,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:36.89,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Maria Ross is denying all charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.06,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Collect all data concerning her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.78,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,However, do it in strict secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.07,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.04,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Hey lady, could you wrap up these flowers for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.29,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, are you going on a date? You lady-killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.31,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you wait, Solaris?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.06,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:22.40,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dying to see you, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:25.69,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to hearing your interesting stories again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:03.33,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The sacrificial lamb is engulfed in the flames of hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:07.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and leaves the boy with feelings of hate and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:12.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And the man reaches out to the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:17.35,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:20.35,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 17, Cold Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,All is playing into the hands of the unknown.
